            The issue was discussed during the passage of the <a href="/bills/export-control-bill">Export Control Bill</a>. A proposal by Lord Campbell-Savours, which was not supported by the Quadripartite
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_169wh' title='Col. 169WH &mdash; HC Deb 27 March 2003 vol 402 c169WH' name='column_169wh' href='#column_169wh' rel='bookmark'>169WH</a>
